            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> remaining white wine vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a crack of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
