      "instruction": "<p>Add a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> to the crushed potatoes with the <strong>pea pesto</strong> and <strong>remaining refreshed peas</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined – these are your <strong>pea pesto potatoes</strong></p>",
